#. I18N: WTHB Link
msgid "This fallback link is used, when no specific context link was defined."
msgstr ""
"Deze terugval-link wordt gebruikt wanneer er geen specifieke contextlink is "
"gedefinieerd."

msgid "Data table"
msgstr "Gegevenstabel"

#. I18N: WTHB Link table
msgid ""
"The context is established by assigning the routes used in webtrees to the "
"corresponding sections in the manual."
